data.description: Don't miss this lovely home with one of the largest floor plans in the community! This two-story townhome exudes a modern 70's vibe w/ a two-story living room & retro stair rail. Relax near the wood burning fireplace & entertain in the formal dining room w/ cocktails from the wet bar. Dining room could be converted into a den. Enjoy the light & bright kitchen w/ newer shaker cabinetry & a gas range that overlooks a kitchen nook or possible family room. Upstairs features a primary bedroom w/ attached bath & walk in shower, plus two other bedrooms & a hall bathroom. This is one of the largest floor plans in the community. Unwind on the private patio off the kitchen that leads to the two-car garage. This amazing community sits on 12 acres of beautiful grounds w/ a community pool, clubhouse & community garden. It is next to Red Fox Trailhead leading into Tryon Creek State Park with 14 miles of hiking trails & 3-mile bike trail. With top rated schools & proximity to downtown Lake Oswego?s shopping & restaurants, this is an unbelievable location. Must be owner occupied.
